<plot>Set in the war years, it tells the story of a Jewish refugee from a transport. She hides on a farmhouse and being a doctor saves one of the family members. A young man on the farm falls for her, but braggs about it too much and collaborators come nosing around. After a shootout between the collaborators and partisans, the girl takes off with the partisans.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?395539</url></doc>
